br />\n仲要段片好似譯錯哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T18:06:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T18:20:20.000Z","msg":"明明個陣都算多人討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n綜合返幾個月前10週年Event嘅消息<br />\n公佈新機設<br />\nExia Repair 4<br />\nDynames Repair 3<br />\n<br />\n公佈新人設<br />\n拉迪茜亞 艾迪 (有提子DNA, 記憶嘅復制變革體)<br />\n哈姆太郎 (冇死加入咗天人, 部分身體同ELS融合)<br />\n<br />\n聲優演出幾段劇場版後嘅小故事<br />\n都幾正幾好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n公佈2019高達00舞台劇化<br />\n故事劇情演員未知<br />\n<br />\nEvent最後有播到彩蛋<br />\n就係樓主個段剎那同Lockon<br />\n不過段片啲英文錯到離譜<br />\n剎那係話佢自己唔可以係Lockon死後嘅世界存在<br />\n所以請求Lockon係個邊代佢生存落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45706830ff7527e256f3238a422dc286e21ca576","tid":731992,"uid":86019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T18:25:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/08/022118_7532450e5e030be940818dcd8eaf5917.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F08%2F022118_7532450e5e030be940818dcd8eaf5917.jpg&h=07a8866c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n只係早幾日kids station同animax播 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n4月活動當日嘅夜晚已經有日場嘅網上付費播放<br />\n大陸有人錄咗傳哂出去所以唔係咩新料 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c5e5bb37e9cbd8d614d5c272598b4ea5088a056","tid":731992,"uid":140835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T18:26:07.000Z","msg":"Event完咗之後水島有係Twitter講咗幾句<br />\n話佢的確有打算做續作<br />\n想要原班人馬一齊做<br />\n但佢自己工作排到好密<br />\n唔會係近期做到續作<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">而且一切要睇SUNRISE頭</span></span><br />\n<br />\n即係要等SUNRISE點頭批准先搞得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我覺得起碼要15週年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f1919cd7a0d8b46ec33550c282c68b243d1cd2b","tid":731992,"uid":36915,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T18:40:27.000Z","msg":"屌你老媽內容出左好耐樓主係邊個次元反黎"}]}